quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  7,59,"Gom…óii Men Nulii Nuuhu e yim…ďe makko …ďen, o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, rewee Alla. Rewetee…óo alanaa on ko woori Mo. Min mi…óo hulani on lepte √Ďalaande mawnde"
  7,60,"Hooree…ďe mbatu yim…ďe makko …ďen wi'i : \"Menen me…óen yi'e e nder majjere …ďanngunde"
  7,61,"O maaki : \"Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, majjere (woo) alaa e am ; ko woni min, ko Nulaa…óo immorde ka Jey…óo Winndere nden"
  7,62,"Mi…óo yottina e mon Nule Joomi am, mi…óo laa…ďana on (reedu), mi…óo anndi ka Alla ko on anndaa"
  7,63,"E on haawi fii waaju no ari on immorde ka Joomi mon e dow gorko jeyaa…óo e mo'on?! Fii yo o jertin on e fii yo on rento, belajo'o, on (he…ďay) yurmeende [Alla]"
  7,64,"∆Āe fenni mo. Men da…óndii mo e …ďen wonndu…ďe e makko ka laana, Men yooli …ďen fennu…ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen. Pellet, …ďe laatino yim…ďe wumi…óu…ďe"